<----------------------------------------------------------------------Voice-controlled-email-bot------------------------------------------------------------------------------>

PLS NOTE: INCLUDES GUI AND USE PYCHARM

DOWNLOAD PYAUDIO,SPEECH RECOGNITION,PYTTSX3 libraries before running the program.

Automating the process of mailing has several advantages and controlling the mail by voice will add to the variety of people who can access the mailing system. 
Automating mails can help people commuting via cars to send mails using voice.
people who previously could not access mailing facilities like the differently-able can also now access mail since it is voice controlled.


